<!--CUSTOM TAGS LIST (in case i missed any, i think the majority is self explenatory)-->

<!--MULT/MULTM/CHIPS/ACTIVATE || used only to determine which give stats and which don't-->
<!--VALUE || used for EID, to determine if a value needs to be shown-->
<!--NEWFLOOR/NEWROOM || when changing floors/rooms-->
<!--ROOMCLEAR || when a room is cleared-->
<!--BOUGHT || when shop/devild deals are bought-->
<!--ITEMS || when a collectible is added/removed-->
<!--REMOVAL || when a trinket is removed (usually the trinket with the tag)-->
<!--HEARTS/COINS/bombs/keys || when said pickup is touched-->
<!--REVIVE/CHANCHEREVIVE || REPENTOGON built-in tags to give the revive HUD-->
<!--CARDUSE/ACTIVEUSE || when a card/item is used-->
<!--TAKEN || when player takes damage-->
<!--PICKUPNUM || when player's pickups values change (OnUpdate callback)-->
<!--CARDS || when a card is obtained/removed (includes cards,runes and pills)-->
<!--ROCKS || when a rock is destroyed-->
<!--RESTOCK || when a shop item is restocked-->
<!--GIVESCOINS || increases its cost when appearing in the mod's challenge-->

